{"id":"7758","user":{"id":"117492","nickname":"亦舟","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FsEnKJerhNpeEolozd_6MDHX3Y1e?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第二期 基于EasyGui的Python图形界面入口","content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ff00ff\" size=\"5\">【前言】</font><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本期给大家介绍Python图形用户界面编程，也就是平常说的GUI，那些带有按钮、文本、输入框的窗口编程，相信大家都不会陌生。&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">&nbsp;迄今为止有很多Python的GUI工具包可以选择，这次就以EasyGui为栗子&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font><font size=\"5\"><font color=\"#008000\">【正式开始】</font></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;一、 获得EasyGui</font><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">方法1(推荐)： &nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">在cmd中输入 pip install easygui安装完成就可以了</font><font size=\"1\"> (没错就是这么简单)&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">方法2：&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">进入EasyGui官网：<a href=\"http://easygui.sourceforge.net&nbsp;\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://easygui.sourceforge.net&nbsp;</a></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">点击中间的Download来到下载页面，</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">接着点击这个链接进行下载，</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"3\">压缩包解压到桌面后，用cmd转到这个文件夹，输入 &lt;你的Python路径&gt;\\python.exe setup.py install （&lt;&gt;里的内容要换成实际数据），例如我输入的是：</font>&nbsp;<span>C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python36\\python.exe setup.py install</span></p>\n<p><span><font size=\"4\">二、导入EasyGui&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>双击运行Python IDLE，Ctrl + N新建一个.py文件，输入以下代码：&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FksygAfa6o44Yj9KeR7V8BLQYNEy\"><span><br></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>如果使用这种最常见的import导入，那么在使用EasyGui的函数时，就必须要在前面加上前缀 easygui F5运行，会弹出这样一个对话框： &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqiweDz6NKgetUlr_isSKtP3XA27\"><span><br></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>另一种种导入方法就是选择导入整个 EasyGui的包，</span><span>然而输出的效果是一样的：</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fh-2iL6cN_Pl33KCCeN3GwDLgxG6\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>而第三种方案则是使用类似上边的import语句：</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>import easygui as g&nbsp;</span><span>这样的话可以将函数前面的easygui. 写成 g. （这里的 g 可以替换成任何一个字母，我这里是GUI的意思）代码如下：</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjT8YPTeKpuc34Qaxkf-KVd4TU2N\"><span><br></span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;（第二部分就到这里拉！）&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span><font size=\"4\">三、利用EasyGui制作出一个界面小游戏</font></span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span>&nbsp;先放代码：&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FuY8SBnwts0K7q0UnekPzjRPo2Ee\"><span><br></span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>1：新建一个欢迎的信息对话框。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>2：我们新建2个变量： title，用它可以给我们的GUI窗口命名，msg，用来储存一个字符串，一个列表 choices，来存放选择。然后新建一个 选择 对话框：choicebox，括号里分别调用这三个变量的信息。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>3：接着新建一个显示结果的信息对话框，将choice转为str类型，和前后2个字符串进行拼接。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>4：最后新建一个ccbox，也就是有 Continue 和 Cancel 这两个按钮，如果点击Continue就继续循环，否则退出。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;运行的结果如下：</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqjedMBPqaqys0q5gBCevCHe64_O\"><span><br></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Ftt6MS6lRm0bfYBjM5aKeASSVwwi\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FicHVl7en_jL5xf0NufrzCaVN_SR\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fo3ZcIaMr5gIpFDHpjKinfNuVj3M\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1511591893,"created_at":1511589462,"n_views":346,"n_replies":3,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":true,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}